<main class="content">
  <h1>🚀 Cybersecurity Career Tips</h1>
  <p>Whether you're self-taught, just starting, or switching careers, here's your roadmap to break into the cybersecurity and bug bounty world.</p>

  <hr>

  <h2>🎓 Do You Need a Degree?</h2>
  <ul class="resource-list">
    <li>No. Many successful hackers and researchers are self-taught.</li>
    <li>However, a degree may help in traditional corporate or government roles.</li>
    <li>What truly matters: <strong>your skills, projects, and proof-of-work</strong>.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>💼 Entry-Level Roles to Target</h2>
  <ul class="resource-list">
    <li>Security Analyst / SOC Analyst</li>
    <li>Vulnerability Assessment Engineer</li>
    <li>Penetration Tester (Junior)</li>
    <li>Bug Bounty Hunter (Freelancer)</li>
    <li>IT Support → Security (Transition path)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>🧠 Build Skills Before Applying</h2>
  <ul class="resource-list">
    <li>Practice on <a href="https://tryhackme.com/">TryHackMe</a> and <a href="https://hackthebox.com/">HackTheBox</a></li>
    <li>Get certifications like <strong>eJPT</strong> or <strong>PNPT</strong></li>
    <li>Create a <strong>portfolio website</strong> with writeups and tools you’ve used (just like you're doing now!)</li>
    <li>Document findings and learning via a <strong>GitHub repo</strong> or blog</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>🛠️ Where to Find Jobs</h2>
  <ul class="resource-list">
    <li><a href="https://infosec-jobs.com/">Infosec Jobs</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://remoteok.com/remote-cybersecurity-jobs">RemoteOK</a> – for remote roles</li>
    <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/">LinkedIn Jobs</a></li>
    <li>Join Indian Telegram groups & Discord servers (e.g. THM India, Hackers Chat)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>💸 Bug Bounty as a Career</h2>
  <ul class="resource-list">
    <li>Start with low-hanging fruit on platforms like <a href="https://bugcrowd.com/">Bugcrowd</a> or <a href="https://hackerone.com/">HackerOne</a></li>
    <li>Focus on public programs and scope you understand (like WordPress or mobile apps)</li>
    <li>Read bounty writeups to learn new techniques</li>
    <li>Join platforms like <a href="https://intigriti.com/">Intigriti</a> (offers EUR payouts)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>📢 LinkedIn + GitHub = Power Combo</h2>
  <ul class="resource-list">
    <li>Post your writeups, lab progress, and findings regularly</li>
    <li>Engage with others in cybersecurity for visibility</li>
    <li>Upload tools, scripts, notes to GitHub to show consistency</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>🔥 Final Advice</h2>
  <ul class="resource-list">
    <li>Consistency > Intelligence — keep learning every day</li>
    <li>Don’t compare your path with others — just <strong>build</strong></li>
    <li>Contribute to the community and help others</li>
    <li>Always stay ethical and responsible</li>
  </ul>

  <p>🎯 You’re now ready to start a real career in security! Keep leveling up, and check back to the <a href="/resources">Resources</a> page for new tools and platforms.</p>
</main>

